
aiff.hwp
========

This plugin enables Hollywood to load and play AIFF sound files. After this plugin has been installed,
Hollywood's OpenMusic() and LoadSample() commands will 'automagically' be able to read AIFF sound
files as well.


History
=======

Version 1.2:    (04-Feb-18)
- New: Added build for the 64-bit Android platform
- Fix: Potential memory access fault

Version 1.1:    (10-Jun-15)
- Fix [Linux/MacOS]: Plugin is now compiled as position-independent code (PIC)
- Fix [OS3]: FPU version will cleanly exit now in case there is no FPU

Version 1.0:    (03-Mar-15)
- First release 


